# <type>(optional-scope): <short summary>
#
# Body: explain why the change is needed and anything reviewers should know.
# Footer: include issue links or breaking-change notes when relevant.
#
# Types:
# feat: user-facing feature
# fix: bug fix
# docs: documentation only
# test: test coverage only
# refactor: behavior-preserving code change
# chore: tooling, release, or maintenance
#
# Examples:
# feat(preorders): add customer pickup notes
# fix(api): reject duplicate open preorder windows
# chore(release): v2.0.1
